headname   )     (*(((struct headname *)((head)->tqh_last))->tqh_last))
 

#define CVM_COMMON_TAILQ_NEXT (  elm,
field   )     ((elm)->field.tqe_next)
 

#define CVM_COMMON_TAILQ_PREV (  elm,
headname,
field   )     (*(((struct headname *)((elm)->field.tqe_prev))->tqh_last))
 

#define CVM_COMMON_TAILQ_REMOVE (  head,
elm,
field   ) 
 

Value:

do {                \
    if ((CVM_COMMON_TAILQ_NEXT((elm), field)) != NULL)          \
        CVM_COMMON_TAILQ_NEXT((elm), field)->field.tqe_prev =       \
            (elm)->field.tqe_prev;                  \
    else {                                  \
        (head)->tqh_last = (elm)->field.tqe_prev;           \
        CVM_COMMON_QMD_TRACE_HEAD(head);                \
    }                                   \
    *(elm)->field.tqe_prev = CVM_COMMON_TAILQ_NEXT((elm), field);       \
    CVM_COMMON_TRASHIT((elm)->field.tqe_next);              \
    CVM_COMMON_TRASHIT((elm)->field.tqe_prev);              \
    QMD_TRACE_ELEM(&(elm)->field);                      \
} while (0)
